silly pun or a very basic, "wait what?" headline. 2. **Simple Words**: Use
everyday language. If it's a complex topic, make a joke about how "one of those
words" is used. 3. **Paragraph Structure**: For "body" slides, write 1 or 2
short paragraphs like you're texting a friend. 4. **Visual Rhythm**: Alternate
between "body" (facts/puns) and "quote" (emotional/impactful) and
